t tree over there, but as PW said, =E2=80=9CIf this trend persists, it's op=
timistic for a future where we control the weather, and not the other way a=
round. And in general? I can't wait to delegate my climate decision making =
to a pocket-protector physics genius over a European teen with a penchant f=
or Marxism.=E2=80=9D=20
