6px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">A 60 year old man German man is now the 7th perso=
n to be &#8216;cured&#8217; of HIV after a stem-cell transplant, despite th=
e donor having only one copy of a mutation in the CCR5 gene, not both. It w=
as previously thought that both copies of the mutated gene are necessary fo=
